Covering Shield						CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat			PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Shield Focus	PREMULT:1,[PREVARGTEQ:PreStatScore_DEX,13],[PREVARGTEQ:FeatDexRequirement,13]						PRETEXT:Dex 13, Shield Focus, Shield Proficiency.															DESC:You can use your shield to protect your most vulnerable parts from area effects.						SOURCEPAGE:p.24			BENEFIT:While using a shield of the type to which your Shield Focus feat applies, you gain a bonus on Reflex saves against area of effect attacks equal to your shield's base bonus to armor class plus any bonuses granted by feats or class abilities. This does not transfer any enhancement bonuses on a shield to Reflex saves.
